"prefixes that are used by a Character to style displayables. Similar to "
"what, who, and window, if \"logo\" is in this variable, properties like "
"logo_xpos and logo_background will cause the logo and background properties "
"to be set on the displayable with id \"logo\"."
msgstr ""

