msgid ""
"Ren'Py has been changed to make a copy of the screens being displayed before "
"a transition occurs. This makes it possible to use a transition to show "
"screen updates. For example, one could increase the value displayed by a "
"bar, and then use the dissolve transition to dissolve in the new segment of "
"bar."
