"to 644 and 755 as appropriate. Prior versions of Ren'Py used 666 and 777 as "
"the permissions, which lead to a security problem when the file was unpacked "
"by a tool that didn't respect the user's umask. (Info-zip had this problem.)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/changelog.rst:2444
msgid ""
"Auto-hinting for fonts is now enabled by default. This restores font "
"rendering compatibility with prior releases."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/changelog.rst:2447
